  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the effectiveness of telemedicine multifaceted
      intervention in symptoms patients with chronic obstructive pulmonary disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study is a randomized clinical trial for patients with chronic obstructive pulmonary
      disease from a primary care. The purpose is to determine the effectiveness of telemedicine
      (teleconsultation and telemonitoring) in control of chronic obstructive pulmonary disease
      symptoms.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
